quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  33,59,"Prophet, tell your wives and your daughters and women of the believers to draw their outer garment near over themselves. That is more likely that they are recognized and are not harassed. And God is forgiving and merciful"
  33,60,"If the hypocrite and those who have a disease in their hearts and those who spread false rumors in the city do not stop, We shall provoke you against them, then they will only be your neighbors in there for a short while"
  33,61,"They are cursed, and wherever they are found they are taken and they are killed"
  33,62,God’s way about those who passed away in the past. And you never find any change in God’s way
  33,63,"People ask you about the hour, say: its knowledge is only with God. And how would you know, the hour may be near"
  33,64,Indeed God cursed the disbelievers and has prepared a burning fire for them
  33,65,"remaining in there forever and ever, and they do not find any protector or any helper"
  33,66,"In a day that their faces are turned over in the fire, they say: we wish we had obeyed God and obeyed the messenger"
  33,67,"And they say: our Master, we obeyed our leaders and our elders (and great ones), and they misled us from the way"
  33,68,"Our Master, give them double the punishment and curse them, a great curse"